口述实录 | 武汉来沪老爸说：谁来要人，你就把我交出去！。
When Wuhan came to Shanghai with his father, he said, "Whoever comes to the party, you must give me up."
黄政、金姬。
Huang Zheng, Jin Ji.
新民周刊                      。
Xinmin Weekly.
新民周刊。
Xinmin Weekly.
深度和角度——这就是我们能做的。
Depth and angle - that's what we can do.
